<taxonomicName box="[329,498,374,401]" class="Dothideomycetes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Fungi" order="Microthyriales" pageId="31" pageNumber="118" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="order">Microthyriales</taxonomicName>
. Epiphyllous fungi.
</paragraph>
